/* Cloud Relay setup — key-free server command (Phase 3 A+C) */
"No API key needed — the helper reads it from Syncthing’s config.xml. Replace /PATH/TO/syncthing with your Syncthing config folder (often ~/.local/state/syncthing or ~/.config/syncthing). Permission error? Add -u <uid>:<gid> for the user that owns config.xml." = "无需 API 密钥——助手会直接从 Syncthing 的 config.xml 读取。请将 /PATH/TO/syncthing 替换为你的 Syncthing 配置文件夹（通常是 ~/.local/state/syncthing 或 ~/.config/syncthing）。遇到权限错误？请为拥有 config.xml 的用户添加 -u <uid>:<gid>。";

