"This purchase needs approval (Ask to Buy). Cloud Relay activates automatically once it is approved. If it was declined, you can simply subscribe again." = "此购买需要批准（购买前询问）。批准后 Cloud Relay 会自动激活。如果被拒绝，你可以直接重新订阅。";
