"Wake-ups went quiet. If there were no vault changes recently, this is normal — the helper only sends when something changes. Otherwise the most common cause is force-quitting VaultSync from the app switcher — iOS then blocks wake-ups until the next manual launch. Also check that the helper on your server is still running." = "唤醒信号沉寂了。如果最近没有 Vault 更改，这是正常的——助手只在有更改时发送。否则最常见的原因是在应用切换器中强制退出了 VaultSync——iOS 会在下次手动启动前阻止唤醒。也请检查服务器上的助手是否仍在运行。";
"Notification permission is not required for this. Check that the iPhone is online and signed in to an Apple Account, then reopen the app so push registration can retry." = "此功能不需要通知权限。请检查 iPhone 是否联网并已登录 Apple Account，然后重新打开应用，推送注册会自动重试。";
